      "duration": 0.98,
      "size": 15696,
      "text": "欢迎来到插值实验。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 30960,
      "text": "假设你有几个测量数据点，想知道它们之间的值是多少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.66,
      "size": 26496,
      "text": "或者你想画一条平滑的曲线通过这些点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/yunxi/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.46,
      "size": 23328,
      "text": "插值正是解决这类问题的数学方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/yunxi/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29520,
      "text": "插值是构造一个函数，使它精确通过给定的数据点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/yunxi/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "与回归不同，插值曲线必须经过每一个数据点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/yunxi/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.02,
      "size": 32256,
      "text": "最简单的插值是线性插值：用直线连接相邻的点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/yunxi/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "但我们通常需要更平滑的曲线，这就需要更高级的方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "lagrange",
      "line_id": "lag-1",
      "filename": "lagrange-lag-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/yunxi/lagrange-lag-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "拉格朗日插值用一个多项式来通过所有数据点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "lagrange",
      "line_id": "lag-2",
      "filename": "lagrange-lag-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/yunxi/lagrange-lag-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.42,
      "size": 22752,
      "text": "n个点可以确定一个n-1次多项式。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "lagrange",
      "line_id": "lag-3",
      "filename": "lagrange-lag-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/yunxi/lagrange-lag-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "这个方法简单优雅，但有一个问题：龙格现象。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "lagrange",
      "line_id": "lag-4",
      "filename": "lagrange-lag-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/yunxi/lagrange-lag-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "当点数增多时，多项式在边缘可能会剧烈振荡。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "spline",
      "line_id": "spline-1",
      "filename": "spline-spline-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/yunxi/spline-spline-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.74,
      "size": 27792,
      "text": "样条插值用分段多项式来避免龙格现象。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "spline",
      "line_id": "spline-2",
      "filename": "spline-spline-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/yunxi/spline-spline-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.45,
      "size": 39168,
      "text": "最常用的是三次样条：每段是三次多项式，在连接点处光滑。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "spline",
      "line_id": "spline-3",
      "filename": "spline-spline-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/yunxi/spline-spline-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "样条这个名字来自绘图员用的弹性木条。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "spline",
      "line_id": "spline-4",
      "filename": "spline-spline-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/interpolation/yunxi/spline-spline-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.55,
      "size": 24768,
      "text": "它在计算机图形学和CAD中被广泛使用。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "interpolation",
      "section_id": "application",
      "line_id": "app-1",
      "filename": "application-app-1.mp3",
